{"data":[{"name":"78:1","price":"彼ら（不信仰者*たち）は何について、尋ね合っているのか？","arabic":"عَمَّ يَتَسَآءَلُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5673,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿamma yatasāalūna ","translations":["About what","are they asking one another","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿamma","yatasāalūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1240],[2,1240,6345]]}},{"name":"78:2","price":"偉大なる消息¹について（、である）。","arabic":"عَنِ ٱلنَّبَإِ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5674,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「偉大なる消息」とは、死後の復活を伝えるクルアーン*のこと（ムヤッサル５８２頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿani al-naba-i al-ʿaẓīmi ","translations":["About","the News","the Great","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿani","al-naba-i","al-ʿaẓīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,490],[2,490,1920],[3,1920,5045]]}},{"name":"78:3","price":"彼らはそこにおいて、意見を異にしている¹。","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي هُمۡ فِيهِ مُخۡتَلِفُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5675,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「意見を異にしている」には、「ある者はそれを嘘と決めつけ、またある者はそれを疑った」「それを魔術、詩、占い師の言葉などと異なる言葉で表現した」「ある者はそれを信じ、ある者はそれを信じなかった」といった解釈がある（イブン・ジュザイ２：５２７－５２８参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī hum fīhi mukh'talifūna ","translations":["(About) which","they","(are) concerning it","(in) disagreement","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","hum","fīhi","mukh'talifūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,1480],[3,1480,2310],[4,2310,5875]]}},{"name":"78:4","price":"断じて（、復活は嘘では）ない！やがて、彼らは（自分たちが噓呼ばわりしたことの結末を、）知ろう。","arabic":"كَلَّا سَيَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5676,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā sayaʿlamūna ","translations":["Nay","(soon) they will know","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","sayaʿlamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,960],[2,960,3975]]}},{"name":"78:5","price":"更に、断じて（、復活は嘘では）ない！やがて、彼らは（自分たちが噓呼ばわりしたことの結末を、）知ろう。","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَيَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5677,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma kallā sayaʿlamūna ","translations":["Then","Nay","(soon) they will know","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","kallā","sayaʿlamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1190],[2,1190,2240],[3,2240,6115]]}},{"name":"78:6","price":"われら*は大地を、（平坦な）寝床（のよう）にはしなかったのか？","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَجۡعَلِ ٱلۡأَرۡضَ مِهَٰدٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5678,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alam najʿali al-arḍa mihādan ","translations":["Have not","We made","the earth","a resting place","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","najʿali","al-arḍa","mihādan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,730],[2,730,1220],[3,1220,2600],[4,2600,3915]]}},{"name":"78:7","price":"また、山々を（堅固な）杭のように？","arabic":"وَٱلۡجِبَالَ أَوۡتَادٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5679,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-jibāla awtādan ","translations":["And the mountains","(as) pegs","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-jibāla","awtādan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1430],[2,1430,3775]]}},{"name":"78:8","price":"また、われら*はあなた方を（様々な）種類¹に創造し、","arabic":"وَخَلَقۡنَٰكُمۡ أَزۡوَٰجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5680,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「種類」の解説には、「男女」「様々な色」「美醜（びしゅう）、背の高低など、対になった、あらゆる種類のこと」といった諸説がある（アル＝クルトゥビー１９：１７１参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wakhalaqnākum azwājan ","translations":["And We created you","(in) pairs","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wakhalaqnākum","azwājan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1940],[2,1940,4045]]}},{"name":"78:9","price":"あなた方の眠りを休息とし、","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا نَوۡمَكُمۡ سُبَاتٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5681,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wajaʿalnā nawmakum subātan ","translations":["And We made","your sleep","(for) rest","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["wajaʿalnā","nawmakum","subātan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1290],[2,1290,2730],[3,2730,4515]]}},{"name":"78:10","price":"夜を衣とし、¹","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا ٱلَّيۡلَ لِبَاسٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5682,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　識別章４７の訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wajaʿalnā al-layla libāsan ","translations":["And We made","the night","(as) covering","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["wajaʿalnā","al-layla","libāsan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2070],[3,2070,3885]]}},{"name":"78:11","price":"昼を生計（の手段）とし、","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا ٱلنَّهَارَ مَعَاشٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5683,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wajaʿalnā al-nahāra maʿāshan ","translations":["And We made","the day","(for) livelihood","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wajaʿalnā","al-nahāra","maʿāshan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1180],[2,1180,3140],[3,3140,4945]]}},{"name":"78:12","price":"あなた方の上に、（割れ目一つない）強固な七層（の天）を築き上げ、","arabic":"وَبَنَيۡنَا فَوۡقَكُمۡ سَبۡعٗا شِدَادٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5684,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wabanaynā fawqakum sabʿan shidādan ","translations":["And We constructed","over you","seven","strong","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["wabanaynā","fawqakum","sabʿan","shidādan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2630],[3,2630,3670],[4,3670,6275]]}},{"name":"78:13","price":"煌々とした灯火¹を置き、","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا سِرَاجٗا وَهَّاجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5685,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「灯火」については、識別章６１の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wajaʿalnā sirājan wahhājan ","translations":["And We placed","a lamp","burning","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["wajaʿalnā","sirājan","wahhājan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1240],[2,1240,2610],[3,2610,5325]]}},{"name":"78:14","price":"絞り時のもの（雨を湛えた雲）から、ざあざあという雨を降らせた。","arabic":"وَأَنزَلۡنَا مِنَ ٱلۡمُعۡصِرَٰتِ مَآءٗ ثَجَّاجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5686,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-anzalnā mina al-muʿ'ṣirāti māan thajjājan ","translations":["And We sent down","from","the rain clouds","water","pouring abundantly","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-anzalnā","mina","al-muʿ'ṣirāti","māan","thajjājan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1930],[2,1930,2540],[3,2540,4440],[4,4440,7030],[5,7030,9245]]}},{"name":"78:15","price":"（それは）われら*がそれで、（人が食べる）種粒と（家畜が食べる）植物を生え出させるため。","arabic":"لِّنُخۡرِجَ بِهِۦ حَبّٗا وَنَبَاتٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5687,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"linukh'rija bihi ḥabban wanabātan ","translations":["That We may bring forth","thereby","grain","and vegetation","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["linukh'rija","bihi","ḥabban","wanabātan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,1810],[3,1810,3290],[4,3290,5235]]}},{"name":"78:16","price":"そして、（いくつもの枝が交差して）重なり合った農園を。","arabic":"وَجَنَّٰتٍ أَلۡفَافًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5688,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wajannātin alfāfan ","translations":["And gardens","(of) thick foliage","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["wajannātin","alfāfan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2200],[2,2200,4115]]}},{"name":"78:17","price":"本当に裁決の日¹はもとより、時が定められている。","arabic":"إِنَّ يَوۡمَ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ كَانَ مِيقَٰتٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5689,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「裁決の日」については、整列者章２１の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna yawma al-faṣli kāna mīqātan ","translations":["Indeed","(the) Day","(of) the Judgment","is","an appointed time","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","yawma","al-faṣli","kāna","mīqātan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,1890],[3,1890,2920],[4,2920,3530],[5,3530,5635]]}},{"name":"78:18","price":"角笛に吹き込まれ¹、あなた方が（各々、自分たちの指導者と共に）集団でやって来る日は。","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يُنفَخُ فِي ٱلصُّورِ فَتَأۡتُونَ أَفۡوَاجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5690,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「角笛に吹き込まれる」については、家畜章７３の訳注を参照。尚、これは復活を知らせる一吹きのこと（ムヤッサル５８２頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma yunfakhu fī al-ṣūri fatatūna afwājan ","translations":["(The) Day","(in which) shall be blown","in","the trumpet","and you will come forth","(in) crowds","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","yunfakhu","fī","al-ṣūri","fatatūna","afwājan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,600],[2,600,2190],[3,2190,2360],[4,2360,3390],[5,3390,4880],[6,4880,6855]]}},{"name":"78:19","price":"また（その日、）天は開かれ、（天使*が降臨するための）いくつもの扉（を有するもの）となり、","arabic":"وَفُتِحَتِ ٱلسَّمَآءُ فَكَانَتۡ أَبۡوَٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5691,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wafutiḥati al-samāu fakānat abwāban ","translations":["And is opened","the heaven","and becomes","gateways","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["wafutiḥati","al-samāu","fakānat","abwāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1180],[2,1180,3790],[3,3790,5050],[4,5050,7055]]}},{"name":"78:20","price":"山々は動かされ、（それから粉々にされて）蜃気楼のようになる。¹","arabic":"وَسُيِّرَتِ ٱلۡجِبَالُ فَكَانَتۡ سَرَابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5692,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　復活の日*の天変地異の様子については洞窟章４７、ター・ハー章１０５－１０７、蟻章８８、山章９－１０、出来事章５－６、衣を纏（まと）う者章１４、階段章８－９、巻き込む章３、衝撃章４－５も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wasuyyirati al-jibālu fakānat sarāban ","translations":["And are moved","the mountains","and become","a mirage","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["wasuyyirati","al-jibālu","fakānat","sarāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1470],[2,1470,2750],[3,2750,3900],[4,3900,5725]]}},{"name":"78:21","price":"本当に地獄はもとより、（不信仰者*たちに対する）見張りの場である。","arabic":"إِنَّ جَهَنَّمَ كَانَتۡ مِرۡصَادٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5693,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna jahannama kānat mir'ṣādan ","translations":["Indeed","Hell","is","lying in wait","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","jahannama","kānat","mir'ṣādan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,2810],[3,2810,3930],[4,3930,5895]]}},{"name":"78:22","price":"（それは、不信仰において）度を越した者たちの、帰り場所なのだ。","arabic":"لِّلطَّٰغِينَ مَـَٔابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5694,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"lilṭṭāghīna maāban ","translations":["For the transgressors","a place of return","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["lilṭṭāghīna","maāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1660],[2,1660,3365]]}},{"name":"78:23","price":"彼らはそこに長期間、留まる身の上。","arabic":"لَّٰبِثِينَ فِيهَآ أَحۡقَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5695,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"lābithīna fīhā aḥqāban ","translations":["(They will) be remaining","therein","(for) ages","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["lābithīna","fīhā","aḥqāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1370],[2,1370,3700],[3,3700,5615]]}},{"name":"78:24","price":"彼らはそこで、（暑さを冷ます）冷たさも（、喉を潤す）飲み物も、味わうことがない、","arabic":"لَّا يَذُوقُونَ فِيهَا بَرۡدٗا وَلَا شَرَابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5696,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"lā yadhūqūna fīhā bardan walā sharāban ","translations":["Not","they will taste","therein","coolness","and not","any drink","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","yadhūqūna","fīhā","bardan","walā","sharāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,520],[2,520,1890],[3,1890,2960],[4,2960,4090],[5,4090,5410],[6,5410,7245]]}},{"name":"78:25","price":"煮えたぎる湯と膿汁¹の外は。","arabic":"إِلَّا حَمِيمٗا وَغَسَّاقٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5697,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「膿汁」については、サード章５７の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"illā ḥamīman waghassāqan ","translations":["Except","scalding water","and purulence","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","ḥamīman","waghassāqan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,960],[2,960,2600],[3,2600,5185]]}},{"name":"78:26","price":"（それらは、彼らの現世での行いに）相応しい報いとしてのもの。","arabic":"جَزَآءٗ وِفَاقًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5698,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"jazāan wifāqan ","translations":["A recompense","appropriate","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["jazāan","wifāqan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2810],[2,2810,5025]]}},{"name":"78:27","price":"本当に彼らは、清算を望んでおらず、¹","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ كَانُواْ لَا يَرۡجُونَ حِسَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5699,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「望む」に関しては、ユーヌス*章７の同語についての訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"innahum kānū lā yarjūna ḥisāban ","translations":["Indeed, they","were","not","expecting","an account","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["innahum","kānū","lā","yarjūna","ḥisāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1540],[2,1540,2530],[3,2530,2890],[4,2890,4120],[5,4120,5955]]}},{"name":"78:28","price":"われら*の御徴¹をひどく嘘呼ばわりし、","arabic":"وَكَذَّبُواْ بِـَٔايَٰتِنَا كِذَّابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5700,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　クルアーン*のアーヤ*を始めとした、アッラー*からの「御徴」のこと（アッ＝シャウカーニー５：４８６参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wakadhabū biāyātinā kidhāban ","translations":["And they denied","Our Signs","(with) denial","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["wakadhabū","biāyātinā","kidhāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1490],[2,1490,3220],[3,3220,5505]]}},{"name":"78:29","price":"そしてわれら*は、全ての物事を書で数え尽くしておいた¹のだから。","arabic":"وَكُلَّ شَيۡءٍ أَحۡصَيۡنَٰهُ كِتَٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5701,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　ヤー・スィーン章１２とその訳注も参照。尚、この「書」の解釈には、「天使*たちが書き留める、行いの帳簿（ちょうぼ）」「守られし碑板*」という説がある（アル＝クルトゥビー１９：１８２参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wakulla shayin aḥṣaynāhu kitāban ","translations":["And every","thing","We have enumerated it","(in) a Book","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["wakulla","shayin","aḥṣaynāhu","kitāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,970],[2,970,2090],[3,2090,3720],[4,3720,5875]]}},{"name":"78:30","price":"ならば（不信仰者たちよ、自分たちの行いの応報を）味わえ。われら*はあなた方に、懲罰以外の何も上乗せはしまい。","arabic":"فَذُوقُواْ فَلَن نَّزِيدَكُمۡ إِلَّا عَذَابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5702,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fadhūqū falan nazīdakum illā ʿadhāban ","translations":["So taste","and never","We will increase you","except","(in) punishment","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["fadhūqū","falan","nazīdakum","illā","ʿadhāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1870],[2,1870,2510],[3,2510,4700],[4,4700,5720],[5,5720,7775]]}},{"name":"78:31","price":"本当に敬虔*な者たちには、勝利の場がある。","arabic":"إِنَّ لِلۡمُتَّقِينَ مَفَازًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5703,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna lil'muttaqīna mafāzan ","translations":["Indeed","for the righteous","(is) success","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","lil'muttaqīna","mafāzan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1310],[2,1310,3250],[3,3250,4335]]}},{"name":"78:32","price":"農園、葡萄、","arabic":"حَدَآئِقَ وَأَعۡنَٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5704,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ḥadāiqa wa-aʿnāban ","translations":["Gardens","and grapevines","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["ḥadāiqa","wa-aʿnāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2360],[2,2360,4315]]}},{"name":"78:33","price":"（彼女ら自身が互いに）同い年の、胸もふっくらとした女たち、","arabic":"وَكَوَاعِبَ أَتۡرَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5705,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wakawāʿiba atrāban ","translations":["And splendid companions","well-matched","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["wakawāʿiba","atrāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,870],[2,870,3095]]}},{"name":"78:34","price":"（酒*で）満杯の¹盃が。","arabic":"وَكَأۡسٗا دِهَاقٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5706,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　ほかにも、「次々とやって来る」「澄（す）んだ」といった解釈もある（アル＝バガウィー５：２０２参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wakasan dihāqan ","translations":["And a cup","full","(34)"],"transliterationArr":["wakasan","dihāqan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1450],[2,1450,3635]]}},{"name":"78:35","price":"彼らはそこで、戯言¹も嘘の言い合いも、耳にすることがない。²","arabic":"لَّا يَسۡمَعُونَ فِيهَا لَغۡوٗا وَلَا كِذَّٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5707,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「戯言」については、信仰者たち章３の同語の訳注を参照。 ２　山章２３と、その訳注も参照（イブン・カスィール８：３０８参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"lā yasmaʿūna fīhā laghwan walā kidhāban ","translations":["Not","they will hear","therein","any vain talk","and not","any falsehood","(35)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","yasmaʿūna","fīhā","laghwan","walā","kidhāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,540],[2,540,1910],[3,1910,2780],[4,2780,4460],[5,4460,4950],[6,4950,7155]]}},{"name":"78:36","price":"（それらは全て、）あなたの主*からの報い、ふんだんなる贈り物としてのもの。","arabic":"جَزَآءٗ مِّن رَّبِّكَ عَطَآءً حِسَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5708,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"jazāan min rabbika ʿaṭāan ḥisāban ","translations":["(As) a reward","from","your Lord","a gift","(according to) account","(36)"],"transliterationArr":["jazāan","min","rabbika","ʿaṭāan","ḥisāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2150],[2,2150,2880],[3,2880,3960],[4,3960,6530],[5,6530,8385]]}},{"name":"78:37","price":"諸天と大地、その間にあるものの主*、慈悲あまねき*お方（からの）。彼らはかれに対し、（お許しを授かった者以外、）語りかけることが出来ない、¹","arabic":"رَّبِّ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ وَمَا بَيۡنَهُمَا ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنِۖ لَا يَمۡلِكُونَ مِنۡهُ خِطَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5709,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　復活の日*に「話すこと」については、夜の旅章９７の訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"rabbi al-samāwāti wal-arḍi wamā baynahumā al-raḥmāni lā yamlikūna min'hu khiṭāban ","translations":["Lord","(of) the heavens","and the earth","and whatever","(is) between both of them","the Most Gracious","not","they have power","from Him","(to) address","(37)"],"transliterationArr":["rabbi","al-samāwāti","wal-arḍi","wamā","baynahumā","al-raḥmāni","lā","yamlikūna","min'hu","khiṭāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,780],[2,780,2430],[3,2430,3660],[4,3660,4250],[5,4250,6680],[6,6680,7370],[7,7370,9370],[8,9370,10710],[9,10710,11560],[10,11560,13385]]}},{"name":"78:38","price":"魂¹と天使*たちが、列をなして立つ日に。慈悲あまねき*お方が（執り成し¹を）お許しになり、正しいこと²を語った者しか、話すことはないのだ。","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَقُومُ ٱلرُّوحُ وَٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ صَفّٗاۖ لَّا يَتَكَلَّمُونَ إِلَّا مَنۡ أَذِنَ لَهُ ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنُ وَقَالَ صَوَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5710,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「魂」は、ジブリール*のこととされる（ムヤッサル５８３頁参照）。「魂」と呼ばれている所以については、マルヤム*章１７の訳注を参照。 ２　復活の日*の「執り成し」については雌牛章４８、マルヤム*章８７、ター・ハー章１０９とその訳注を参照。 ３　「正しいこと」の筆頭が、シャハーダ*の言葉である（イブン・カスィール８：３１０参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma yaqūmu al-rūḥu wal-malāikatu ṣaffan lā yatakallamūna illā man adhina lahu al-raḥmānu waqāla ṣawāban ","translations":["(The) Day","will stand","the Spirit","and the Angels","(in) rows","not","they will speak","except","(one) who ","permits","[for] him","the Most Gracious","and he (will) say","(what is) correct","(38)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","yaqūmu","al-rūḥu","wal-malāikatu","ṣaffan","lā","yatakallamūna","illā","man","adhina","lahu","al-raḥmānu","waqāla","ṣawāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,995],[2,995,2501],[3,2501,3071],[4,3071,5954],[5,5954,7110],[6,7110,7525],[7,7525,10436],[8,10436,11472],[9,11472,13157],[10,13157,14362],[11,14362,14913],[12,14913,15497],[13,15497,16210],[14,16210,17211],[15,17211,18290],[16,18290,19496]]}},{"name":"78:39","price":"それは、（必ずや起こる、）真実の日。ならば、誰でも（その日の救いを）望む者には、（正しい行い*により、）自らの主*を帰り場所とさせるのだ。","arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ ٱلۡيَوۡمُ ٱلۡحَقُّۖ فَمَن شَآءَ ٱتَّخَذَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّهِۦ مَـَٔابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5711,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"dhālika al-yawmu al-ḥaqu faman shāa ittakhadha ilā rabbihi maāban ","translations":["That","(is) the Day","the True","So whoever","wills","let him take","towards","his Lord","a return","(39)"],"transliterationArr":["dhālika","al-yawmu","al-ḥaqu","faman","shāa","ittakhadha","ilā","rabbihi","maāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1050],[2,1050,1990],[3,1990,3370],[4,3370,3860],[5,3860,6480],[6,6480,7540],[7,7540,8110],[8,8110,9410],[9,9410,11195]]}},{"name":"78:40","price":"本当にわれら*は、あなた方に間近に迫った懲罰を警告した。人が、自分が行った（全ての）ことを目にし、不信仰者*が（清算の恐怖ゆえ、）「ああ、私が土であったらよかったのに！¹」という日の（懲罰を）。","arabic":"إِنَّآ أَنذَرۡنَٰكُمۡ عَذَابٗا قَرِيبٗا يَوۡمَ يَنظُرُ ٱلۡمَرۡءُ مَا قَدَّمَتۡ يَدَاهُ وَيَقُولُ ٱلۡكَافِرُ يَٰلَيۡتَنِي كُنتُ تُرَٰبَۢا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5712,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　その日、人間は懲罰を目にし、自分が現世で（清算を受ける必要のない）土であったならば、と望む。あるいは、その日は動物でさえも集められ、公正な裁きを受けるが、それらはその後に懲罰を受けることなく土と化す。彼らは、自分たちもそのような存在であったなら、と望むのだという（前掲書８：３１０－３１１参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"innā andharnākum ʿadhāban qarīban yawma yanẓuru al-maru mā qaddamat yadāhu wayaqūlu al-kāfiru yālaytanī kuntu turāban ","translations":["Indeed We","[We] have warned you","(of) a punishment","near","(the) Day","will see","the man","what","have sent forth","his hands","and will say","the disbeliever","O I wish","I were","dust","(40)"],"transliterationArr":["innā","andharnākum","ʿadhāban","qarīban","yawma","yanẓuru","al-maru","mā","qaddamat","yadāhu","wayaqūlu","al-kāfiru","yālaytanī","kuntu","turāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,4357],[2,4357,6423],[3,6423,8433],[4,8433,10572],[5,10572,11442],[6,11442,13120],[7,13120,14061],[8,14061,14556],[9,14556,15692],[10,15692,19201],[11,19201,20040],[12,20040,21508],[13,21508,22358],[14,22358,22875],[15,22875,24011],[